Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.governanceaction.mapper

Class OpenMetadataTypesMapper

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.governanceaction.mapper.OpenMetadataTypesMapper
public class OpenMetadataTypesMapper extends Object
OpenMetadataTypesMapper provides property name mapping for the open metadata types. It includes identifiers for all the types.
